<h2>Profile Abuse Report</h2>

<p>A profile has been reported for abuse:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Profile Name:</strong> <%= @profile.name.presence || "Anonymous" %></li>
  <li><strong>Profile UUID:</strong> <%= @profile.uuid %></li>
  <li><strong>Job Title:</strong> <%= @profile.job_title.presence || "Not specified" %></li>
  <li><strong>Profile Bio:</strong> <%= @profile.bio.presence || "No bio provided" %></li>
  <li><strong>Is Public:</strong> <%= @profile.is_public? ? "Yes" : "No" %></li>
  <li><strong>Reported by:</strong> <%= @reporter_email %></li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Profile Links:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <% if @profile.github_url.present? %>
    <li>GitHub: <%= @profile.github_url %></li>
  <% end %>
  <% if @profile.twitter_url.present? %>
    <li>Twitter: <%= @profile.twitter_url %></li>
  <% end %>
  <% if @profile.linkedin_url.present? %>
    <li>LinkedIn: <%= @profile.linkedin_url %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Please review this profile and take appropriate action if necessary.</p>
